plotPoints.content: This is the start of the story! You start in a cave with a sword and shield. You can go left or right. Choose 1️⃣ for left and 2️⃣ for right
You see the exit but there is a evil monster in front of it! Choose 1️⃣ to fight (1d20 roll, roll higher than a 12) or 2️⃣ to run away!
You see an exit! To get there you have to jump over a pit. Choose 1️⃣ to jump (1d20 roll, roll higher than a 14) or 2️⃣ to go back!
You slashed the evil monster and it died. You can savely leave the cave, Congratulations!
You missed your attack! The monster got a hit on you! Choose 1️⃣ to fight again (1d20 roll, roll higher then a 12) and 2️⃣ to run away!
You missed with your sword and the evil monster put his claw in your ribcage. You lay on the ground and die in a few seconds. Beter luck next time!
Oh no! You fell inside a spiked pit and did not make it out alive... Beter luck next time!
You savely jumped over the pit! You can savely leave the cave, Congratulations!
